dc_title_s: North Sea, Netherlands--Germany, Borkum to Texel (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. "From Netherlands and German charts to 1992." "Copyright 1995 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 37223. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA). United States. Defense Mapping Agency. (1995). North Sea, Netherlands--Germany, Borkum to Texel (Raster Image). LandInfo. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/xb379df1796 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
